into a 71-53 lead.  Jennifer Parker scored a career-high 26 points in the loss
for EC.  Rochester shot 52 percent in the second half and outscored Elmira 55
28.  U of R out-rebounded Elmira 52-26.  Kelly Wescott led U of R with 21.
